<h2>What this site is</h2>

<p>This site is the <strong>content hub</strong> for the course. It holds the durable material — units, foundations, references, AI partners, the rubric. Daily workflow — assignments, submissions, grades — lives in <strong>Google Classroom</strong>. The split is intentional: stuff that doesn't change often lives here; stuff that changes daily lives there.</p>

